library(tidyverse)
library(ggplot2)

data = read_csv('data/topic_distribution_year.csv', skip = 1) %>% 
  select(-'...1') %>% 
  rename(year = '...2', topic = '...3')%>% 
  mutate( topic = as.character(topic))

data %>% 
  ggplot(aes(year, mean, color = topic))+ 
  geom_line()

data %>% 
  ggplot(aes(year, median, color = topic))+ 
  geom_line()
